# Emission Engine
Emission Engine is a custom game engine made in order to create *Mad Dream*, a surreal exploring and adventure video game.
Actually, the engine work as a C# framework that you can import. But in the future you will code in Lua and execute from terminal line or with a GUI.
***
### Engine 
It's the main project use for rendering.
Rendering take his foundations on OpenGL and GLFW. It also uses ImageSharp from Six Labors to load images but a custom image loader is intended. 
***
### Model Loader
Emission Engine come with his own model loader.
Currently, it can charge :

 - OBJ Files from Wavefront

***